sentences.sentence: You give a tenth of your spices--mint, dill and cummin.

sentences.sentence: XCEC will be the third Engine joint venture of Cummins in China after Dongfeng Cummins and Chongqing Cummin .
sentences.translation: 西安康明斯是继重庆康明斯和东风康明斯之后康明斯在华的第三个发动机合资项目。
